          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "From Dr. J.Kozempel (2014-08-21): For beam monitoring,",
                "we used both monitor reaction on Ti foil (48-V) and a",
                "Faraday cup, so we detected 0, 34 uA using monitor",
                "reaction and 0, 31 uA using Faraday cup. For the yield",
                "calculation the 0, 31 uA value was used. In any case we",
                "expect the overall beam current uncertainty to be",
                "around 10%."
              ]
            }
          ],
